## Suggested first hour

1. `curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Avarile/cybernetics-agent/master/scripts/install.sh | bash`
2. `cybernetics setup`
3. `cybernetics` — have a real conversation, let it write to `MEMORY.md`.
4. `cybernetics tools` — turn on web search + a terminal backend (Docker if you want sandboxing).
5. `cybernetics gateway setup` for Telegram or Discord, then `cybernetics gateway start` on a small VPS.
6. Schedule one recurring task (e.g. a morning briefing).
7. Watch a skill emerge after a couple of multi-step tasks.

